$interpreted: Alice: ... Was I blown here from the location of the tree?
Alice: Ugh...
Kittyeyes: Sis Nolva!
Nolva: Coming~!
Kittyeyes: Whew~ That was close, but all is well~
Kittyeyes: Sis Nolva, are you injured?
Nolva: No.
Nolva: Little girl, how about you?
Alice: ... I'm alright. Thank you for saving me.
Kittyeyes: No big deal~ We live nearby. We just happen to see you on our way home~
Kittyeyes: ... You, on the other hand...

Kittyeyes: You don't look like a resident of Paradise Prairie.
Why are you sleeping here all by yourself?
Alice: That's because...
Alice: (If I want to save Deemo, her power is necessary as well. Without her, we can't complete the song... but where is she?)
Nolva: Little girl, what's the matter? Are you not feeling well?
Nolva: Kittyeyes, how about we take her to Dr. Clovis——
Kittyeyes: NO! That is absolutely NOT an option!
Nolva: Kittyeyes, you have too much of a bias against Dr. Clovis.
Kittyeyes: I believe myself to be perfectly normal. It's sis Nolva who's way too kind!
Alice: (I remember that when we first arrived, the sister who took us away is...)
Alice: ... Umm, excuse me. Do you know where the princess of this country lives?
Angelia: Look out!
Angelia: Thank goodness I made it on time... Are you alright?
Masked Girl: ......
Angelia: I realize that you are very scared and may be unable to talk right now. It's okay, everything is fine now...

Masked Girl: Stop getting in my way!
I was so close to finally succeeding!
Angelia: You... didn't call out for help on purpose? Why?
Masked Girl: Am I obliged to answer your question just because you saved me?
Angelia: You could have died!
Masked Girl: Idiot, it's not as simple as it seems.
Masked Girl: You guys are part of our dreams. We, on the other hand, are part of another person's dream.
Masked Girl: I just want to do an experiment. If something happened to me here, without me, maybe it'll be impossible for her to ever wake up again...
Masked Girl: Let go of me! Just let me go!
Angelia: The things you said make no sense at all! What do you mean by that!?
Masked Girl: The one who makes no sense is her! It's you! It both of you! Not me!
Angelia: I don't understand what you're talking about. You should calm down first...
Masked Girl: Why do you have to wake up? Why do both of you want to wake up no matter what!?
Masked Girl: Can't we just stay in the dream, forever?

Masked Girl: I was working so hard...
I was trying my best to keep telling lies...
Masked Girl: Tell me! Why!
Angelia: ... You... Did someone tell you about the things between my uncle and me?

Masked Girl: ... I want to stay in the dream.
Once I wake up, everything will come to an end.
Masked Girl: I don't want to lose that person. That's all I ever asked for.
Angelia: ......

Masked Girl: Don't you guys feel sad, like at all?
Is that the reason why no matter how hard I tried to stop you, you still want to wake up?
Angelia: ... No, you're wrong. The people who woke up are also very sad.
Angelia: We don't want to lose people we love as well.
Masked Girl: Liar!!
Angelia: ... Your face...
Angelia: ... So that's why...
Angelia: ... Yes, you felt sad and tired, didn't you? You had to watch us, the ones who knew nothing at all and only cared about dreams.
Angelia: I am sorry. We realized this too late.
Angelia: Sione and Sir Dagger...? What's going on?
Sione: Princess. Umm... to be honest, it's...
Masked Girl: You... why are you... Where's Deemo? Is he with you?
Dagger: My two very trustworthy friends escorted her to me. Heard that the companion she looking for is with Angelia...
Alice: Deemo is in danger. I need you to help me!

Masked Girl: W, why should I help you?
You don't know anything. Every time you try to do something, you only make things worse...
Angelia: ... No need to worry. She will become stronger.
Masked Girl: L, let go of me. What do you want?
Angelia: Prove that you are strong enough. Once you do, she will go with you.
Angelia: Because the person you want to save is a very precious person to her as well. Am I right?
Alice: Is that true?
Masked Girl: ......
Alice: Understood. I will definitely prove it to you!
Alice: I, I won...
Masked Girl: ... Hmph.

Alice: Wait!
You promised that you will go save Deemo with me...!
Masked Girl: You can't do it without me... Hmph, you are indeed useless after all.
Masked Girl: Let's get moving. How much time do you plan to waste here? We'll do this as fast as possible. Deemo must've been waiting for a long time now.
Alice: ... Okay!
